OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWinds will gradually ease
OL,6,Fthrough the day, but scattered,
OL,7,Fblustery showers continue with some
OL,8,Fwith hail and thunder possible,
OL,9,Falthough these less frequent than
OL,10,FWednesday. There will be some bright
OL,11,For sunny spells too. Temperatures
OL,12,Fremaining below average for mid-May.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FThe wind and showers will
OL,15,Fease overnight, becoming mostly dry by
OL,16,Fmorning. Some clear spells developing
OL,17,Funder lighter winds, allowing for a
OL,18,Fchilly end to the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
